    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a new BGP transitive extended community, as well as its usage, to signal prefix origin validation results from an RPKI Origin validating BGP speaker to other BGP peers. Upon reception of prefix origin validation results, peers can use this information in their local routing decision process.</t>
